{"tid":812950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"開咗學一個禮拜已經俾同學排斥","createTime":"2018-09-10T05:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T05:15:48.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1b34fcc4fb543096e588ab6b251844078c12d9","tid":812950,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"頭幾日返學都冇咩問題<br />\n但上個禮拜五上完pe 堂之後啲同學就喺我背後講我壞話<br />\n話我死肥仔，<br />\n又話我有體臭，又話我成面暗瘡好唔乾淨<br />\n咁我青春期有呢啲特徵都好正常姐<br />\n<br />\n啱啱放飯個鐘一響啲同學一支箭咁走晒<br />\n搞到我自己一個孤零零食m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解佢哋會咁現實㗎，其實我心地好好"},{"pid":"a7667960489d7be663999217805122c91ba62b5a","tid":812950,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"車氏膠po再現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d831fcfad1d1ef64510bc8b76e5576e021dd2b79","tid":812950,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"幫QQ"},{"pid":"43f74e8a876ec67d30cf7a172030c392fe0aae9a","tid":812950,"uid":18138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"快d話比老師知有人蝦你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2dd65cbd1b6386c68b981923892d1677dc0b1b3","tid":812950,"uid":145194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"見到依d po仲以為係毒步天下開，入到黎先知唔係"},{"pid":"f4d361d105a2064630dc6d3c92f53631b075029a","tid":812950,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:06:07.000Z","msg":"抵你死啦"},{"pid":"fa1e8b90aa86862853a69bc70e215dffb5f1cfc6","tid":812950,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2dd65cbd1b6386c68b981923892d1677dc0b1b3","tid":8